						<p>Two broken pieces of a slab set up in Pudūr, a hamlet of Nambiyūr.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara Vīra-Nañjaṇṇa-uḍaiyār: Īsvara, Chittirai = 1517 A.D., April (?)</hi></p>						

						<p>This fragmentary inscription now contains only the name of the ruler and the few details of the date given above.</p>						

